title: Price index : Servers in Canada 2016
summary: A line chart about the Price index Servers Canada 2016 in Canada the year 2016 .
Values are analyzed in the different months of the year .
With index values ranging from less than 45000 to more than 60000 .
gold: The price index for servers in 2018 rapidly fell from a high in January , to its lowest point in March of 2016 . After that the price index saw some fluctuation in the coming months until November , where it dropped again and did not change in December .
